string-array.name: health_deep_shallow_sleep_guide_descriptions
string-array.item: Place your phone next to you when you sleep to track body movements and generate sleep cycle stats.
"To get accurate stats, place your phone beside or under the pillow and make sure that it's no more than 50 cm away from your body."
When bedtime schedule is set up, your sleep will be tracked automatically.
Sleep tracking consumes only about 1% of your battery per night.

string-array.name: health_sleep_snore_guide_descriptions
string-array.item: Sound will be recorded while you sleep. Machine learning allows Mi Fitness to detect snoring, talking, and loud noises, and save the recordings on your phone.
Microphone will be turned on and off according to your bedtime schedule.
Make sure your phone is sufficiently charged before you go to bed. Low battery may interrupt sound recording.
